adams.flow.control.Flow
	-annotation
	Demonstrates how to replay archived tweets (twitter export).\nUseful when experimenting with algorithms processing \ntweets and require the same tweet stream each time.
	-actor
		adams.flow.source.TweetReplay
			-replay
				adams.data.io.input.TwitterExportArchive
					-archive
					${EXAMPLE_FLOWS}/data/twitter-archive.csv
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.TwitterConverter
			-converter
				adams.data.twitter.TextConverter
					-separator
					\t
	-actor
		adams.flow.sink.Display
	-flow-execution-listener
		adams.flow.execution.NullListener

